ADDITIONAL NOTICE (educational content)

The handbook materials (under handbook/) and the rendered PDFs (under
rendered/) are AI-generated study aids prepared with Claude Code (Anthropic).
Question stems and official answers are drawn from the Taiwan national medical
licensing examination question bank; all explanations, mechanism notes, IHC
correlations, buzzword mappings, comparison tables, and weak-spot analyses
are AI-authored and may contain factual errors or omissions.

Before using any content for clinical decision-making, formal teaching, or
publication, verify against Robbins Basic Pathology, Robbins & Cotran, and
the current WHO classification series. This material does not substitute for
textbooks or clinical judgment and does not constitute medical advice.
